{
  "name": "CoreClaw Instagram账号情报 / Instagram Intel",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "note-overview",
      "name": "Overview / 概览",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1700,
        -520
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CoreClaw Instagram账号情报 / Instagram Intel\n\n**Purpose (EN):** Instagram profile intelligence.\n\n**用途:** Instagram账号情报.\n\nThis workflow uses the official CoreClaw node as the scraping source and combines standard n8n nodes for polling, deduplication, AI enrichment, routing, reporting, and destination payload preparation.\n\n用途: 以CoreClaw官方节点为数据来源，并结合n8n标准节点完成轮询、去重、AI增强、分流、报告和载荷准备。",
        "width": 760,
        "height": 380
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "note-parameters",
      "name": "Parameters / 参数",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -900,
        -520
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Parameters / 参数\n\nEdit **Input Config / 输入配置** before running.\n\n**Example / 示例:**\n`username=instagram, limit=1`\n\n**Tips / 提示:**\n- Start with low limits for testing.\n- Increase wait_seconds for larger jobs.\n- Select your CoreClaw credential on each CoreClaw node after import.\n- 测试阶段建议使用较小数量.\n- 大批量任务请提高wait_seconds.\n- 导入后请在CoreClaw节点选择你的凭证.",
        "width": 700,
        "height": 380
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "note-flow",
      "name": "Flow / 流程",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1700,
        -120
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Flow / 流程\n\n1. Trigger / 触发\n2. Input Config / 输入配置\n3. Start CoreClaw Run / 启动CoreClaw\n4. Wait + Poll / 等待并轮询\n5. Get Results / 获取结果\n6. Normalize + Deduplicate / 规范化并去重\n7. AI or Enrichment / AI或增强处理\n8. Prepare Payloads + Report / 准备载荷并生成报告\n\nUse **Success Summary / 成功摘要** to inspect final output.\n使用 **Success Summary / 成功摘要** 查看最终输出。",
        "width": 760,
        "height": 360
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "note-output",
      "name": "Outputs / 输出",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -900,
        -120
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Outputs & Integrations / 输出集成\n\n**Output (EN):** Creator/brand account profile, opportunity score, partnership action.\n\n**输出:** 生成可用于业务系统的数据载荷、摘要和执行证据.\n\nRecommended next integrations:\n- Google Sheets / Google 表格\n- Airtable or CRM / Airtable 或 CRM\n- Slack alerts / Slack 提醒\n- Notion database / Notion 数据库\n- Gmail or email outreach / Gmail 或邮件外联",
        "width": 700,
        "height": 360
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "manual-trigger",
      "name": "Manual Trigger / 手动启动",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1460,
        120
      ],
      "parameters": {}
    },
